Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在逐渐改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对教给我各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我相遇的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要由衷地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之类的…超级害羞 我说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 对于诸位顺利完成了所有课程的毕业生们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你们能以从这所历史悠久的学校毕业为荣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我期待你们能时时准备着向未来展翅翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 爱丽丝前辈走过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快去说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？我…我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个…爱丽丝前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你顺利毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如…如果可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把你制服的第二颗纽扣给我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 太谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.82,0:01:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也一直是你的崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真狡猾 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级吓人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像没告诉你们今天是毕业典礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看了毕业于相同学校的前辈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你顺利毕业 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢二位前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年夏天 爱丽丝终于从中学毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像平常一样走路嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得应该那样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这是中学时期最后的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我必须做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒走可是失败了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是超级No problem
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有雅典娜前辈在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间就是静止的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:02.59,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那阵 橙色和风之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤尾舟 要通过了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小后辈 非常有干劲呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 非常地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为以前在学校耽误了的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后都能用来跟前辈们一起练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我…超级高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们也向着正式领航员 Let's go！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是发声练习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤尾舟 要通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那爱丽丝从学校毕业后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在非常有干劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在感觉自己超级能干的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然自己也感觉很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是觉得现在无论做什么都能非常顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊 来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明天去野餐好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次 一定要去成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你在做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当的准备都完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级完美呢 雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一天我来扮演客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝来扮演领航员带我游览吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣的主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受这个建议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那雅典娜前辈现在开始就是我重要的客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位客人 请握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝的笑容变得很自然了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我们好像是初次见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我每天都在跟能够给我最棒的笑容的前辈们练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:08:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一座是仅凭一个桥拱就横跨了48米大运河的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里亚托桥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Ponte di Rialto
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这周围与圣马可广场不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商店 市场 酒店和居民区混杂在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里可以感受到新威尼斯真实的民间生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可说是第二个城镇中心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领航员小姐的观光解说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常清晰易懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我每天都被满口禁止的前辈重点培训呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来您想参观什么地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您有想要参观的景点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就恭敬不如从命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面是一片田园地带
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与这座著名的港口城市有着迥异的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您享受新威尼斯的另一种风情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请各位慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Ciao
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Buon giorno
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 您很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 您想再来杯茶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 不过不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是个野餐的好日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领航员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们差不多该回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 现在刚好在下行中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再稍微等一会就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？领航员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…看上去这么不可靠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 非常可靠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天辛苦你了 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个水上电梯到达顶部之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把工作模式切换掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经做什么都没问题了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确认为在跟前辈们开始练习后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的技术和观光解说是变得有模有样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船歌就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来声音很小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也不太擅长唱歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不知道自己有没有放开声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道自己有没有走调…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是觉得自己必须学好船歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋里就越是一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己觉得唱得很辛苦的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听众自然也会听得很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱歌的技巧当然不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢唱歌这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢…唱歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果连爱丽丝自己都不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还有谁会去喜欢呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领航员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地就在眼前了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗？领航员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说在这颗星球的地表上充满海水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为AQUA之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个世界都是橙色的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在世界被染上橙色的短短这段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这些住在水星的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会觉得非常眷恋 非常感怀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里蕴藏着…我们的永远一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是灯里前辈和蓝华前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有刚才管理水上电梯的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面的是公司的高层人员和凤尾舟协会的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一天真是太感谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领航员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最后能请你唱首歌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领航员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 您知道名扬水星的水之三大精灵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样 我也是其中那位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为风之精灵的领航员的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(398,440)\fs20}Seiren
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得意弟子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我过去不擅长唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我小时候最喜欢的就是唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人的话让我回想起了那时的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公司一直在等着你从中学毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,划船的技术非常完美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都让人担心的观光解说和客人的接待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后连船歌都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在今天的考试里展现出了显著的进步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于担负了水上领航协会下一代重任的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤尾舟协会给予了非常高的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且怀着强烈的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出了前所未有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果断的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 橙星公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:21:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始 你就是正式领航员了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橙星…公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二位前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.36,0:21:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:21:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小后辈～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:21:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.59,0:22:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镌刻在水星历史上的领航员的光辉历程中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又诞生了前所未有的跳级成为正式领航员的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝小姐真的好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.14,0:22:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点崇拜她了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你 爱丽丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝成为正式领航员了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就有这种预感了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我超级超级紧张…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.28,0:24:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候就要让心情放松～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.82,0:24:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份 赏月之夜的心动…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.50,0:24:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请握住我的手
